RESOLUTION RAISING A COMMITTEE TO INFORM SENATOR
MARTIN M. LOONEY THAT THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES IS
ORGANIZED AND READY TO RECOGNIZE HIS DISTINGUISHED
LEGISLATIVE CAREER.
Resolved by this House:
1 That a committee consisting of the New Haven delegation of
2 Representatives be appointed to inform Senator Martin M. Looney that
3 the House of Representatives is organized and ready to recognize his
4 distinguished legislative career.
LCO No. 6109 1 of 1

